Sun Come Up bụ ihe nkiri ihe nkiri nke afọ 2010 banyéré mmetụta nke okpomọkụ ụwa na Carteret Islands. Ihe nkiri ahụ gosipụtara n'afọ 2010 Full Frame Documentary Film Festival n'ubochi asatọ n'ọnwa Eprel. A kpọrọ ya aha dị ka ónyé a họpụtara màkà Academy Award for Best Documentary (Short Subject) na 83rd Academy Awards n'ubochi irí abụọ na ise n'onwa Jenụwarị afọ 2011, mana Strangers No More meriri ya.
